h1. cron

h2. Purpose

A cron trigger that executes based on the defined cron expression

h2. Examples

{code}
class MyJob {
   static triggers = {
      cron name:'cronTrigger', startDelay:10000, cronExpression: '0/6 * 15 * * ?', timeZone: TimeZone.getTimeZone("GMT-8") //timeZone is optional
   }

   void execute() {
      println "Job run!"
   }
}
{code}
